OL,5, Five women who were born in Congo and  
OL,6, separated from their mothers by the    
OL,7, colonial authorities are suing Belgium 
OL,8, for crimes against humanity.           
OL,10,FThe mixed-race women were taken away   
OL,11,Ffrom their black mothers at birth 70   
OL,12,Fyears ago solely on the basis of the   
OL,13,Fcolour of their skin.                  
OL,15,FBelgium controlled the central African 
OL,16,Fcountry from the 19th Century until it 
OL,17,Fwon its independence in 1960.          
OL,19,FMillions of Africans died during       
OL,20,Fcolonial rule.                         
